#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:36
msgid "Your first chain execution — 5-minute walkthrough"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:38
msgid ""
"This walkthrough uses the Heusdenpas chain: three DMNs from SVB, SZW, and "
"the Heusden municipality that together assess eligibility for the Heusdenpas "
"social benefit pass."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:40
msgid "**Step 1 — Open the Chain Builder**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:42
msgid ""
"Click the GitBranch icon in the left sidebar. The view splits into three "
"panels: Available DMNs (left), Chain Composer (centre), and Configuration "
"(right)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:44
msgid "**Step 2 — Verify DMNs are loaded**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:46
msgid ""
"The Available DMNs panel should show several DMN cards. If it is empty, "
"check that the active endpoint is set to the RONL TriplyDB dataset in the "
"configuration panel. You should see `SVB_LeeftijdsInformatie`, "
"`SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie`, and at minimum one Heusden DMN."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:48
msgid "**Step 3 — Build the chain**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:50
msgid ""
"Drag `SVB_LeeftijdsInformatie` into the Chain Composer. Then drag "
"`SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie` below it. The validation panel should show a "
"green checkmark: \"Chain is valid and ready to execute.\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:52
msgid "**Step 4 — Provide inputs**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:54
msgid ""
"The input form in the Configuration panel shows the inputs the chain needs "
"from you. Fill in a `geboortedatum` (date of birth in YYYY-MM-DD format, "
"e.g., `1960-01-01`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:56
msgid "**Step 5 — Execute**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:58
msgid ""
"Click **Execute**. The execution panel shows per-step progress with timing. "
"When complete, the results panel shows the final output values."
msgstr ""

