"health` returns `\"status\": \"healthy\"`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:67
msgid "[ ] DMN list loads in Chain Builder (at least 3 cards)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:68
msgid ""
"[ ] Dragging two DMNs into the composer produces either a green or amber "
"validation status (not an error)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:69
msgid ""
"[ ] An exact-match chain (SVB → SZW) shows green validation and active "
"Execute/Save/Export buttons"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:70
msgid ""
"[ ] Clicking Execute with valid inputs returns results without console errors"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgetting-started.md:71
msgid ""
"[ ] SPARQL Query Editor: clicking Run Query returns results in the table"
msgstr ""

